                    <p>小米・米家多功能便携手电筒 10 月 11 日开售，该款手电筒拥有&nbsp;1000 流明亮度，配备 3100mAh 电池，<strong>售价 99 元</strong>。</p><p>今日京东 11.11 仅需 78 元即可入手：</p><ul class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p>领 200-20 元补贴券：<a href="https://u.jd.com/IGzBnAv" target="_blank">点此领取</a></p></li></ul><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://u.jd.com/IgzLV1n" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img height="800" src="https://img14.360buyimg.com/pop/jfs/t1/182029/19/48761/37003/66f684baF42bbdbea/b566f254186000dd.jpg" title="上市 1 月立打 8 折：小米米家多功能便携手电筒京东新低" width="800" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">京东</span><span class="card-name">小米 米家便携强光手电</span></span><span class="card-abstract">超长续航</span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price">加购物车 1 件</span><span class="card-btn-deep">领 10 元券</span></span></span></span></a></dir><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://u.jd.com/Irz1dSK" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img height="800" src="https://img14.360buyimg.com/pop/jfs/t1/223610/26/37869/9419/65703120F0ce989b2/c4c9f39490c6ccf3.jpg" title="上市 1 月立打 8 折：小米米家多功能便携手电筒京东新低" width="800" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">京东</span><span class="card-name">凑单品 下单后可申请退款</span></span><span class="card-abstract"></span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price">加购物车 1 件</span><span class="card-btn-deep">直达链接</span></span></span></span></a></dir><p>另外，即日起京东可领至高 11111 元无门槛红包，再省一笔更划算：<a href="https://u.jd.com/IOzlVsc" target="_blank">点此抽红包</a>。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="706" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/10/9913bce0-44f1-42de-9a59-79ab2e1e17a8.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="上市 1 月立打 8 折：小米米家多功能便携手电筒京东新低" width="591" /></p><p>据介绍，小米米家多功能便携手电筒直径约 <strong>3cm</strong>、重约 <strong>125g</strong>，内置 <strong>3100mAh 容量锂电池</strong>，可提供最高约 30 小时续航。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img